{"id":88406,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/废除农地集体所有制，把土地还给农民/","date":"2010-08-03T08:22:00Z","modified":"2010-08-03T08:22:00Z","title":"废除农地集体所有制，把土地还给农民","content":"<p><p align=\"left\"><span>中国改革开放</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>年，经济增长奥妙之一就是土地生财，各级政府炒卖土地。由于土地产权和宪政法治的缺失，中国土地管理产生大量严重腐败现象。</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span>以上海的一宗腐败案为例。上海第一中级法院以受贿、巨额财产来源不明、滥用职权和私藏弹药数罪并罚，判处前上海房屋土地资源管理局副局长殷国园死刑，缓期</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>年执行，没收个人全部财产，其妻陈伟以受贿罪判处有期徒刑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>年，并处没收财产人民币</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span><span>万元。殷国园案发前已退休，到上海土地学会任会长。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1995</span><span>年，殷国园任上海土地批租和旧城改造副局长，受贿的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>千</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>百</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">71</span><span>万元中，有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>千</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>百</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">80</span><span>万来自地产商人江信惠。殷批给陈良宇之弟陈良军两块土地造成土地出让金及收益损失</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>千</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>百余万元，陈良军倒卖 ……</p>\n<p>……</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span></p>\n<p><span></p>\n<p><span></p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></p>\n<p></span></span></span></p>\n<p></span></p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://blog.ifeng.com/article/6706816.html\" title=\"废除农地集体所有制，把土地还给农民\">废除农地集体所有制，把土地还给农民</a></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[]}